Subject: Re: [T2] Sliding Door Seal, how do I get it behind the door

I have always just cut the seal (bottom side) and glued the ends back
together with the weatherstrip adhesive. Otherwise, you have to take off the
middle support arm. Way to many opportunities to bung something up when
handling the slider by yourself.

